  "title": "Part Time Cafe Service Crew",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Part-Time Service Crew</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Mon - Fri: up to $12/hr</p>\n<p>- Weekend: up to $14/hr</p>\n<p>- PH 1.5x</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>• Greet customers with a friendly attitude.</p>\n<p>• Take orders and handle cashier duties.</p>\n<p>• Ensure accurate data entry in the POS system.</p>\n<p>• Prepare and serve food and beverages according to customer orders.</p>\n<p>• Maintain shop cleanliness and follow food hygiene standards.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• No experience needed; entry-level candidates welcome.</p>\n<p>• Team player with a pleasant personality and good communication skills.</p>\n<p>• Capable of multitasking in a fast-paced environment.</p>\n<p>• Willing to work weekends and holidays.</p>\n<p>• Able to commit minimally 4 days or 32 hours a week (including weekends)</p>\n<p>• Able to commit at least 3 months</p>\n<p>• Food Hygiene Certification preferred.</p>",
